{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/react-native/react-native-apk사이즈-줄이기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Dryad","author":"dryad","siteUrl":"https://dryadsoft.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"dryadsoft/dryadsoft.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ee9455cc-12ef-5025-a0b0-de9aa18b04e8","excerpt":"React Native 시작하기 1. build.gradle 수정하기 변경전 변경후 2. Hermes 사용하기 필수 설치 패키지\nMicrosoft Visual C++ 2015 Redistributable android/app/build.gradle 파일 수정 만약 ProGuard를 사용한다면 proguard-rules.pro 파일에 아래 문구 추가 모두 설정되었으면 기존 빌드된 내용은 삭제한다.(Window에서 명령어) 앱 실행","html":"<p><a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/getting-started\">React Native 시작하기</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-buildgradle-수정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-buildgradle-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 buildgradle 수정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>1. build.gradle 수정하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>변경전</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">def enableSeparateBuildPerCPUArchitecture <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\ndef enableProguardInReleaseBuilds <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>변경후</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">def enableSeparateBuildPerCPUArchitecture <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\ndef enableProguardInReleaseBuilds <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-hermes-사용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-hermes-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 hermes 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\">true</a>2. Hermes 사용하기</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ol>\n<li>필수 설치 패키지\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=48145\">Microsoft Visual C++ 2015 Redistributable</a></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>android/app/build.gradle 파일 수정</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">  project.ext.react <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      entryFile: <span class=\"token string\">\"index.js\"</span>,\n-     enableHermes: <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>  // clean and rebuild <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> changing\n+     enableHermes: <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>  // clean and rebuild <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> changing\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>만약 ProGuard를 사용한다면 proguard-rules.pro 파일에 아래 문구 추가</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">-keep class com.facebook.hermes.unicode.** <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> *<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>모두 설정되었으면 기존 빌드된 내용은 삭제한다.(Window에서 명령어)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> android <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> gradlew clean</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>앱 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">npx react-native run-android</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"React Native apk사이즈 줄이기","date":"November 08, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react-native/react-native-apk사이즈-줄이기/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/gulp.js/gulp---uglify를-이용하여-babel로-컴파일된-javascript-파일-축소하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gulp - uglify를 이용하여 babel로 컴파일된 javascript 파일 축소하기","category":"gulp.js","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/gulp.js/gulp---javascript를-babel을-이용하여-컴파일하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gulp - javascript를 babel을 이용하여 컴파일하기","category":"gulp.js","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}